between the S and the GS\nregion. The net effect of the uncertainty affecting observed quantities, on the\nposition of sample objects on the (Mv-Mp) plane, is also investigated. Finally,\na principle of corresponding states is formulated for macrogases with assigned\ndensity profiles and scaled truncation radii.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2009 15:40:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 May 2010 08:49:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
